29:21.326 --> 29:22.930
Claudette said no...

29:23.094 --> 29:25.267
...on account of
her Constitutional rights.

29:25.430 --> 29:27.967
Before she knew it,
she was dragged from that bus...

29:28.133 --> 29:30.204
...by force by the Montgomery police.

29:30.368 --> 29:34.145
That was nine months
before Rosa Parks did the same thing.

29:34.305 --> 29:37.775
